									James Mathe on May 23, 2015
									                                

                                
									Reply ‚Üì                                


                            The best start/end days of a campaign are Monday-Thursday when people are around their computers and/or work computers. The above information was a bit out of date so I updated it. I wouldn‚Äôt start on a Sunday or end on a Friday anymore. The goal is to start/end when you know people are not doing other things and they are likely to be online. Weekends are very bad for that sort of thing.

                        
                    
                    


                

                
                
                        
                        
							
                        
                    
                    
                    
                        
                            
